item.title: TED Talks – Tim Berners-Lee: The next Web of open, linked data
item.description: For everybody who is asking: “What’s the next step in internet evolution?” This presentation of Tim Berners-Lee could give you the anser. Linking Data is one of the most exciting initiatives going on right now. Enjoy the presentation! (via TED)
